org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.handlers
Class AeWsdlReference

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.handlers.AeWsdlReference
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeCatalogListener, IAeWsdlReference
public class AeWsdlReference
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeWsdlReference, IAeCatalogListener

Holds information obtained from wsdl def for the service desc object. Allows the wsdl to be replaced "under the hood". If this happens, any cached properties obtained from the wsdl will be flushed and the service desc's operations will be updated.
